metadata.name: The Foggy Trees #141
metadata.description:
This is the second project exploring the possibilities of fictional trees. I used only two elements, the sun and the trees, to outline the whole picture.

There are 7 kinds of total number of trees (between 1 and 34 of Fibonacci series). Each generative token have one of three fork rates, giving the trees a different look. Finally, in addition to the no tint ones, there are 6 tint colors to give them different vibes.

Made with p5js.

Please follow me on Twitter: luyotw

Controls:
- Press ‚Äúf‚Äù to toggle the frame, there is my signature on the mat inside the frame.
- Press ‚Äús‚Äù to save the image displayed at that moment.

metadata.name: Unicorn #7784
metadata.description:
All of us have dreams, and everyone would like to meet a fairy, a genie, a wizard, or someone else who will make our dreams come true in a snap of a finger or with the wave of a wand. But we're the only ones who can do it. We are those magical unicorns, unique, inimitable, with our own qualities and magical abilities.
These unicorns are the visualization of our inner selves that makes our dreams come true. An embodiment of all the best with a huge positive magical power.

Twitter: @unicorn_nft_art
Web: https://unicorn-nft.web.app/

by @lucky26puch, @AgataBaranova17
